# GitHub Actions Monitor — xbar plugin config
#
# Each line: owner/repo  workflow name
# The workflow name must match exactly as shown in `gh workflow list`.
#
# To use: copy this file to one of:
#   ~/.xbar-github-actions.conf        (default, committed via .symlink)
#   ~/.xbar-github-actions.local.conf   (machine-specific override, not committed)
#
# If the .local.conf file exists, it takes precedence entirely.

